\c 105
\s Izimangaliso zeNkosi eyazenzela abantwana bakoIsrayeli
\p
\v 1 Bongani iN\nd kosi\nd*, libize ibizo layo\x + 1 Lan. 16.8-22. Hlab. 78.106.\x*\x + Isa. 12.4. 1 Lan. 16.34.\x*, lazise phakathi kwezizwe izenzo zayo\x + Hlab. 145.12.\x*.
\v 2 Hlabelelani kuyo, lihlabelele amahubo kuyo, likhulume ngezenzo zayo zonke ezimangalisayo.
\v 3 Zincomeni ebizweni layo elingcwele; kayithokoze inhliziyo yabadinga iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 4 Dingani iN\nd kosi\nd* lamandla ayo, lidinge ubuso bayo njalonjalo\x + Hlab. 63.2.\x*.
\v 5 Khumbulani izenzo zayo ezimangalisayo eyazenzayo, izimangaliso zayo lezahlulelo zomlomo wayo\x + Hlab. 72.18.\x*,
\v 6 nzalo kaAbrahama inceku yayo\x + 105.43. Hlab. 106.5,23. 105.26. 1 Lan. 16.13.\x*, bantwana bakaJakobe abakhethiweyo bayo\x + 105.43. Hlab. 106.5,23.105.26. 1 Lan. 16.13.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Yona iyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu; izahlulelo zayo zisemhlabeni wonke.
